Post-Match Reflections: Andrew Moore: What a performance. They have thrashed Australia. That is a mighty effort.

Stuart Clark: There is some soul searching to do for the Australians. The tournament isn't over but they are going to have to improve their performances. Their next match is an absolute crucial match.
